        "content": "<p>I found myself wanting <code>wrapAsync</code> for <code>MetaM</code>. While it's easy to write this by hand by getting the state and context, I was wondering if using <code>controlAt</code> is appropriate here:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Lean</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">open</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Lean</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Meta</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">@[</span><span class=\"n\">inherit_doc</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Core</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">wrapAsync</span><span class=\"kd\">]</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Lean</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Meta</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">wrapAsync</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">act</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Unit</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">→</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">MetaM</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">α</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">MetaM</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">EIO</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Exception</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">α</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">do</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">controlAt</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">CoreM</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">fun</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">run</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">Core</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">wrapAsync</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">fun</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">do</span>\n<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"n\">run</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">&lt;|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">act</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
