    {
        "content": "<p>Is this the same as:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">@[</span><span class=\"n\">inherit_doc</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Core</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">wrapAsync</span><span class=\"kd\">]</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Lean</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Meta</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">wrapAsync2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">act</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Unit</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">→</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">MetaM</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">α</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">MetaM</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">EIO</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Exception</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">α</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">do</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">metaCtx</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">readThe</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Meta</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Context</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">metaSt</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">getThe</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Meta</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">State</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">Core</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">wrapAsync</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">fun</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">_</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">act</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">()</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">|&gt;.</span><span class=\"n\">run'</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">metaCtx</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">metaSt</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>or is there some <code>ST.Ref</code> trickery here with multiple threads?</p>",
